Package nl.pim16aap2.util.reflection

Class EnumValuesFinder

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.util.reflection.ReflectionFinder<Object[],EnumValuesFinder>
nl.pim16aap2.util.reflection.EnumValuesFinder
public class EnumValuesFinder extends ReflectionFinder<Object[],EnumValuesFinder>
Represents a ReflectionFinder for enum values.

This class can be used to retrieve enum values.

Calls should be chained, as the instance can change between invocations of some methods.

Author:
Pim
